These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, disaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | family   |
| Sport         | badminton | baseball |
| Transport     | tram | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, nectarine
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical
2 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, boat
1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | pumpkin     | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | time-travel  |
| Pet           | turtle         | hamster     |
| Transport     | car   | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, bartender
2 different pets are kept: fish, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, car
1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the bartender##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | 7up     | coffee |
| Job         | bartender | chef    |
| Pet         | fish         | goat        |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | car    |

