3. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | mirinda |
| Food          | cucumber   | apricot  |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | country         |

