.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, mechanic
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, australian
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the mechanic is the indian##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | mechanic | designer    |
| Nationality   | indian       | australian |
| Pet           | rabbit         | turtle    |
| Sport         | rowing    | ice-hockey   |

